The paper deals with channel estimation in massive MIMO systems, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of several CS subfields. However, the focus on coordinated pilot design and the use of fractional programming techniques suggest that the paper is most likely to be classified under Information Theory (cs.IT). Other possible sub-categories include Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Signal Processing (cs.SI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Multimedia (cs.MM).
